These buildings house various shops and restaurants, inviting passersby to explore their offerings. People can be seen walking on the sidewalks, going about their day, while cars are parked neatly on the side of the road. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cityscapes. The sky itself is overcast, casting a soft light over the scene.
